Description: Well.... It's a pretty simple map designed for GunGame servers, everything in that map can break (the "houses" that is) so its pretty much a map for short rounds, if you know what i mean. There are no buy zones cause the map is designed for GunGame servers. 

Extract Files to: 
C:\Programmer\Steam\steamapps\account_name\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

If you like the map rate it! (or if you dont lol)
